name: Velvet Floral Vintage Millinery Headband
description:
My personal favorite headband created with three vintage millinery flowers is a perfect adornment.  The floral piece is backed with soft felt for a smooth surface and adhered to a thin elastic for comfort.  Wee ones to adults love these pieces to add a touch of sophisticated pizazz. 

This piece is currently available in 12 months to adult.  As these are vintage and handmade, quantities are very limited and come and go based on availability.

If purchasing as a gift, please leave your note to the lucky recipient in PayPal's note to sender box.
